# Default card container — Onyx / PlanFinanceContainer

For **new** interactive cards, list rows, and grid tiles in `apps/mobile/`, use
**Onyx container** — `OnyxContainer` (`components/OnyxContainer.tsx`), alias of
`PlanFinanceContainer`. See also `onyx-container.mdc`.

Reference implementations: `StockHoldingTile`, `WealthHoldingTile` in `PatrimoineHoldingsSections`,
`HubLoansSection` obligation rows, `PlanCard`.

## Shell (do not hardcode hex)

- **Component**: `<PlanFinanceContainer halo? style={…}>…</PlanFinanceContainer>`
- **Fill / outline**: `useAppTheme().colors.containerBackground` + `containerBorder`
- **Radius**: 13px (`PLAN_FINANCE_CONTAINER.borderRadius` / `planFinanceKit.radius.card`)
- **Border**: `StyleSheet.hairlineWidth`
- **Halo**: on by default — `planFinanceCardHalo` from `constants/planFinanceKit.ts`
- **Style-only** (no halo): `planFinanceContainerShellStyle(colors)` from `planFinanceKit`

## Press feedback

Wrap in `Pressable`; on pressed use `planFinanceContainerPressedStyle()` (opacity **0.82**).
Do not put opacity on the container itself.

## Interior padding

| Layout | Helper | Values |
|--------|--------|--------|
| Full-width row (icon + copy + amount) | `planFinanceContainerRowLayoutStyle()` | `padding: 12`, `gap: 12`, row flex |
| 2-column compact tile (stocks) | `planFinanceContainerCompactTilePaddingStyle()` | H/T 12px, bottom 14px |
| Full plan card | `PLAN_FINANCE_CONTAINER.padding.card` | 20px |
| Vertical list gap between rows | `PLAN_FINANCE_CONTAINER.listGap` | 8px (`spacing.sm`) |

## When NOT to use

- Dashboard alert cards, account balance rows, glass inputs → `containerSurfaceStyle()` in `theme.ts` (1px border, 18px radius, no halo)
- `TransactionDetailSheet.tsx` — protected; do not modify unless explicitly requested

## Bad — duplicated inline shell

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — reimplements PlanFinanceContainer
<View style={{
  backgroundColor: '#111111',
  borderRadius: 13,
  borderWidth: StyleSheet.hairlineWidth,
  borderColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.12)',
}}>
```

## Good

```tsx
import { PlanFinanceContainer } from '@/components/plans/PlanFinanceContainer';
import {
  planFinanceContainerPressedStyle,
  planFinanceContainerRowLayoutStyle,
} from '@/constants/planFinanceKit';

<Pressable style={({ pressed }) => [pressed && planFinanceContainerPressedStyle()]}>
  <PlanFinanceContainer style={planFinanceContainerRowLayoutStyle()}>
    {children}
  </PlanFinanceContainer>
</Pressable>
```

Tokens: `PLAN_FINANCE_CONTAINER`, `planFinanceCardHalo` in `constants/planFinanceKit.ts`.
